Summary:
User can see the reviews driven from the database, but it would be better if he/she can also write his own reviews. User would feel more attached to the application.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Click on the ‘Ant-Man’ movie on the Feed screen Most Popular Movie category.
Result: User gets information about the movie, but only he/she can do is put it in favorites. No other interaction is provided.